{"tid":597221,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"她問變成IU要雷射幾次？　醫美爸「誤傳」惹網友笑噴飯XD","createTime":"2018-03-18T12:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T08:27:01.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a5e1ee977591ad0e3cd5ae23abe22a3cabd2f45","tid":597221,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2402/2402141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2402%2F2402141.jpg&h=91a86146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲老爸等級很高阿...。（圖／網友提供，請勿隨意翻拍，以免侵權，下同。）<br />\n<br />\n網搜小組／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n幽默又毒舌的老爸，真是讓人又愛又恨阿！一名女網友家裡在做醫美行業，加上最近突然想打雷射，便傳訊息向爸爸打聽療程問題，就在她問打幾次會變IU時，被老爸「神吐槽」，讓網友全笑翻，直呼「太可愛啦」。<br />\n<br />\n女網友在Dcard說道，「最近覺得自己太醜了，這幾天要回家想說試試看有沒有救，先問了一下我爸，結果...。」只見她問1個療程要幾次，老爸認真回覆道，「雷射一般是5次，針愛打幾次就幾次，有病治病、無病強身，至於價錢...哼哼，別跟你媽商量」。"},{"pid":"72b551ca0bab4b5b8a804da00f6b1f94f79ef561","tid":597221,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2402/2402142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2402%2F2402142.jpg&h=1f2766a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒多久，原PO接著問，「那我要打幾次才會變成...」，並貼出IU的照片，沒想到老爸直接說，「打死重練」，然後又趕緊回，「誤傳...，大概10到幾10次，術後保養也很重要，雷射是破壞，刺激皮膚再生，如果術後不好好照顧，也是枉然」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，原PO冷笑著說，「還給我誤傳，謝謝嘲諷技能點滿」；而網友們看完紛紛回應，「還很正經的打了誤傳呢」、「分明是故意（壞笑」、「好歡樂的一家人」、「先被妳爸爸爸爸爸爸爸爸爸爸笑死」、「羨慕家裡做醫美」。"},{"pid":"5dde2b2e3ce0eec122b8ff174534bd001f2115b5","tid":597221,"uid":163554,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02c62fa73104d4767216231023bc5f96b03f5a88","tid":597221,"uid":40588,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"同屋企人send message都係新聞<br />\n<br />\n個記者破碎家庭出身？"},{"pid":"d784da919b3a025ebf12fa4aadfd8eb710e7bf07","tid":597221,"uid":40337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"有咩好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c8179c58e7f30f9bff419f14074e5043389104","tid":597221,"uid":85924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc9f036f03522243f9f78b6b9c5061a59ba8648","tid":597221,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"(笑）"},{"pid":"757f37ae3db3027b64b314a13a314563196d08f4","tid":597221,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"打你老母臭西咩做雞啦"},{"pid":"cf10442fb226e6da47b30fae58b7cd752d07df14","tid":597221,"uid":118508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:06:35.000Z","msg":"岩啦 打死重練 下世做韓國撚啦 <br />\n嫁個韓國老公 成世承受大男人主義"},{"pid":"17ad2d4c213c3302a6f9e478832942d563d1c52a","tid":597221,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:27:01.000Z","msg":"嘩我屌你老母<br />\nsor 誤傳"}]}